MALALANE –  A G4S security van was ambushed this morning by 15 men. J&M Security operations manager Shaun Terblanche said the suspects shot at the security vehicles tyres causing them to stop.  “They held up the guards, took their firearms and bombed the van for the money.” Nobody was injured during the heist. The suspects were last seen heading in the direction of Schoemansdal in a gold Amarok and a silver grey Mercedes Benz.  